Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gatherall the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The land of herancestors\nwas destroyed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and heryounger brother, Kohaku,\nhas fallen into Naraku's hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:18.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Sango has a cute, dependable friend,\NKirara, who's always by her side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:21.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:22.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourfriend Kirara is a feline\ndemon with two tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When she battles, she grows\nin size and even flies through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:13.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But usually, she has the appearance\nof a lovable, little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's very good-natured and endures\nthe willful ways of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But once in a while, you should\nteach everyone a lesson, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:51.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No.\N- Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something wrong with Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I woke up to find her gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe she went for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara isn't one to go\noff without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then she ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe she's in heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's at that rebellious stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!\NDon't make Sango worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara seemed herusual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just 'cuz she's gone awhile\nain't no reason to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't be worrying about\nevery little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave her alone and\nshe'll be back in awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry!\NKirara's not a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now it'd be different\nwith anotherkid I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Just who do\nyou mean, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who else?! There's only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, Sango...\nthis fish is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who said she'd be right back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She hasn't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! How was I to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:33.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Have you forgotten\nwhat you said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say that again, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No use searching senselessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where Inuyasha steps in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:56.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara's plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She uses this to eat cat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what'm I supposed to do\nwith that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you should sniff it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already know Kirara's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do yourbest, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope. The scent ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After only three steps?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, let's split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:36.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Useless! The end of her scent means\nthat she flew away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't catch any scent\nof Kirara around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, we can't just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, don't you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like you had a fight or Kirara\nknows someone around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like she lost her appetite...\nor was moody lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or maybe there's a large patch\nof catnip growing nearhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe... it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:18.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I always go to battle and drag her along\nwithout thinking twice about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we need to go a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we take herforgranted\nand ride her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I make hergo on errands\nand don't reward her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even her favorite fish...\nshe only gets a rare treat of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, don't blame yourself\nso much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara's not the type\nto run away over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The reason Kirara disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Inuyasha teased me earlier,\NI realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's obvious when\nyou think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it? Tell us, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara had enough of\nall of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Come out and say it\ninstead of dragging it out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put yourhand on yourheart\nand think hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you truly say that you have\nnever been mean to Kirara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll outline yourvery acts\nof thoughtlessness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In orderto masterthe\NBacklash Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:48.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you practiced the Wind Scar\non Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scarpractice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind... Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:23.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara! You all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bald spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll all grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, time to eat! Let's go eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thinking back,\nshe did have some bald spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you thought no one was watching,\nyou're mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of you, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara's bald spots were\ncaused by you, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's putting all the blame\non me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly! Kirara's probably forgotten\nall about it by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you're saying there's\nanother cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, don't say you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... young village girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's time foryou to appear\non the scene, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Such a cute kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hername is Kirara.\NShe's my kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As are you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Oh dear!\N- Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a manly monk you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please spend the night\nin this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No mine!\N- Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, you're needed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil spirit begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw you, Miroku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, you're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara is ourfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't take advantage of her.\NRememberthat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you nevertook advantage\nof her, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, what'll I do?\NWhat'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not anothertest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Test? No, I don't have a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you hearmy plea,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll give you flounder and\ntuna-flavored cat treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw you, Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you go back home\nthat time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:15.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but please wait there.\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, wait. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,HAPPY BIRTHDAY GRANDPA!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:39.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came back, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are. My present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But unlike that water imp hand,\nthis is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can stay awhile today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a special occasion!\NNow let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A special occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A special occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A special occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A special occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of which,\NI completely forgot the treats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even you, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you've learned\nyourlesson
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and won't be mean\nto an innocent demon ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Especially Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you evergive me\na noogie again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't get Kagome's snacks\nfor one week!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not for you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, don't misunderstand.\NWe just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We didn't mean anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm in no position\nto criticize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:13:59.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd turn overin my sleep\nand smother her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I'm in a bad mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd make her fly across\nthe night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd make her transform just\nso she could light the camp fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grab her paws several times\na day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pinch her nose while\nshe was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dress her up just for kicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:30.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What WE did was tame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a foolish human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To even think you could leave\nmy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This forest has so little food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! I came here thinking\nit was Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it's only a baboon wannabe\nand a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey mister... get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Anotherdemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bastard, you dare let my prey go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I smell Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The scarf I gave Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bones are scattered all over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:24.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!\NDid you eat Kirara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fools! As if I'd rememberwho\NI've eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you eat her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll let you\njoin herright away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in my belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything here is my ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:56.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He uses the counteraction of the\ntree branches to move at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he attacks from a high altitude\nwhich is always fail-safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wasn't just boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only Kirara were here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:26.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. From now on,\nyou must take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just a petty demon\nthat jumps around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} avenge Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think that you can defeat me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:38.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,simply by taking down\nthe tree branches!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should have cherished Kirara\nmore dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara... Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making us worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai bade me bring a\nwhetstone for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awhetstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you carry such\na heavy stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I asked Kirara to\nhelp bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:34.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came all this way and\nrode Kirara back to Totosai's hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a tough commute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirara! It's been a long time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's sudden,\nbut I need yourhelp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What're you doing\nat this hour?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo! Tell Inuyasha and\nthe others{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I'm borrowing Kirara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be back in one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,B-But what about that scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What're you doing, Kirara?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't have any time to waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:41.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I... probably...\nwas half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-asleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hope you're ready forthis, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help me, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Not too hard.\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Miroku!\NSango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad, Sango.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at the sky!\NNice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo! Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:48.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've lost my {\i1}shinidama.{\i0}\NLeave me and justgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:54.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you go alone,\nyou may get out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't give up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In orderto escape,\nwe have to join forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Kikyo and Kagome: Alone in the Cave"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, the warmth of someone who lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the source of\NKagome's strength?
